<emphasis box="[990,1145,1521,1544]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">C. jaliscoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
holotype frontal view. 2, Same lateral view of left paramere. 3, 
<taxonomicName box="[764,927,1555,1578]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Ceraspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oaxacaensis">
